{{Infobox magazine | title = Nadie | logo = Nadine Magazine Logo.gif | logo_size = 180px | image_file = <!-- cover.jpg (omit the "file:" prefix) --> | image_size = <!-- default is 180px --> | image_alt = | image_caption = {{deletable image-caption|Wednesday, 20 September 2017|F6}} | editor = Aouni Kaaki | editor_title = <!-- up to |editor_title5= --> | previous_editor = | staff_writer = | photographer = | category = General | frequency = Weekly | format = A4 | circulation = | publisher = Dar El Shark | paid_circulation = | unpaid_circulation = | circulation_year = | total_circulation = 65,000 | founder = | founded = 1980 | firstdate = {{Start date and age|1980|01|11}} | finalnumber = | company = Dar El Shark | country = [[Lebanon]] | based = Minet el Hosn, [[Beirut]] | language = Arabic, Lebanese Arabic | website = | issn = | oclc = }} '''''Nadine''''' ({{lang-ar|نادين}}:{{IPA-ar|nādin}} or ''''' Nadine Magazine''''' : {{lang-ar|مجلة نادين}} {{IPA-ar|majal'lat o nādin|}}) is weekly social Lebanese magazine publishing by Dar El Shark, from 1980. <ref>{{cite web|title=El-Shark Lebanese Newspaper|url=http://www.elsharkonline.com/NadineMode.aspx|website=www.elsharkonline.com}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|title=Nadine Magazine|url=https://www.yelleb.com/company/291162/nadine-magazine|website=Yelleb}}</ref> Interested to star society, the latest gossip, fashion trends, interior design and health and beauty. == Criticism == Nadine has been criticized many times.<ref>{{cite web|title=مجلة نادين تحيي الأموات|url=https://www.lbcgroup.tv/news/d/lifestyle/202503/مجلة-نادين-تحيي-الأموات/ar|website=www.lbcgroup.tv}}</ref> In August 2017, [[Layal Abboud]] condemned an issue of Nadine Magazine for its depiction of her [[Female body shape|chest and face shape]] with the words, "Bigger than this chest" emblazoned on its cover, accused the magazine of trying to increase readership by [[dumbing down]] and [[Oversimplification|oversimplifying]] its content.<ref>{{cite web|title=Episode 29 – Layal Abboud Interview|url=https://www.lbcgroup.tv/watch/chapter/27354/47577/layal-abboud-interview/en|website=lbcgroup.tv|publisher=[[Lebanese Broadcasting Corporation International]]|accessdate=24 August 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=لبنان: عنوان بتلميحات جنسية لمجلة حول صورة ليال عبود يثير جدلاً واسعاً.. والفنانة ترد: قصدي شريف!|url=https://arabic.cnn.com/entertainment/2016/04/10/layal-abboud-magazine-cover|website=arabic.cnn.com|publisher=CNN Arabic|accessdate=24 August 2017}}</ref> == Complaints on Nadine == * November 2004: [[Suzanne Tamim]]. <ref>{{cite web|title=المحكمة تؤجل النظر في شكوى سوزان تميم ضد مجلة ''نادين''|url=https://www.albawaba.com/ar/ترفيه/المحكمة-تؤجل-النظر-في-شكوى-سوزان-تميم-ضد-مجلة-نادين|website=البوابة|language=ar|date=7 November 2004}}</ref> * May 2007: [[Najwa Karam]]. <ref>{{cite web|title=إدانة مجلة نادين بجرم الذم بنجوى كرم ويوسف حرب|url=http://www.alanba.com.kw/ar/last/11338/18-05-2007-ادانة-مجلة-نادين-بجرم-الذم-بنجوى-كرم-ويوسف-حرب|website=alanba.com.kw|language=ar}}</ref> * [[Ragheb Alama]] filed a [[lawsuit]] against Nadine, Accused of "Spreading false news, intimidation and slander", <ref>{{cite web|last1=للإعلام|first1=الوكالة الوطنية|title=حكم للمطبوعات بتغريم صحافيين في مجلة نادين في دعوى راغب علامة|url=http://www.nna-leb.gov.lb/ar/show-news/122018/حكم-للمطبوعات-بتغريم-صحافيين-في-مجلة-نادين-في-دعوى-راغب-علامة|website=الوكالة الوطنية للإعلام|language=ar}}</ref> * May 2017: [[Sherine]]. <ref>{{cite web|title=شيرين عبد الوهاب تواجه دعوى قضائية في لبنان|url=http://www.paparazzieg.com/286754|website=باباراتزي}}</ref>
